title: Kristen Schaal
description: Kristen Schaal (Flight of the Conchords! Comedy! Toy Story 3!)! HOLY COW! One of Pete's favorite people and comedians stops by to make it very weird as a part of the ongoing no-AC Sleepy Summer Series and boy do we have some laughs, some real talk, and some overshares. Just a delight. Please enjoy you weirdos!!
